description.en: StakeWise is a liquid Ethereum staking protocol that tokenizes users' deposits and staking rewards as sETH2 (deposit token) and rETH2 (reward token). All tokens are mapped 1:1 to ETH in the Pool and can be used as a representation of staked Ether in the DeFi ecosystem.
